Copy the public key as authorized_keys in the current directory
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
cp /root/.ssh/id_rsa.pub authorized_keys

Build the Custom CentOS Ansible image
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
docker build -t tektutor/ansible-centos .

Test if the image got built successfully by
docker images
